
UI NEVER calls services directly
UI NEVER modifies state directly

UI → Controller → State → UI

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

        UI (pdf_upload_component)
                    ↓
        file selected (QFileDialog / upload widget)
                    ↓
        event generated (on_pdf_selected)
                    ↓
        DocumentController.handle_pdf_upload()
                    ↓
        PDFExtractionService.extract()
                    ↓
        DocumentController processes result
                    ↓
        AppStateStore.update_document()
                    ↓
        State updated:
            - doc
            - doc_hash
            - metadata
            - chat_history = []
                    ↓
        Signals emitted from AppStateStore
                    ↓
        UI components receive updates:
            - pdf_info_component refreshes (pages, method, chars)
            - chat_history_component clears messages
                    ↓
        UI reflects new PDF state

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------


            UI (chat_input_component)
                        ↓
            user enters text + presses "Send"
                        ↓
            event generated (on_send_message)
                        ↓
            ChatController.handle_user_message()
                        ↓
            AppStateStore.append_user_message()
                        ↓
            State updated:
                - chat_history += user message
                        ↓
            Signal emitted
                        ↓
            chat_history_component updates UI (shows user message)
                        ↓
            ChatController calls LLMService.chat()
                        ↓
            LLM response received
                        ↓
            AppStateStore.append_assistant_message()
                        ↓
            State updated:
                - chat_history += assistant reply
                        ↓
            Signal emitted
                        ↓
            chat_history_component updates UI (shows assistant message)

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

        UI (sidebar button: "Remove PDF")
                    ↓
        event generated
                    ↓
        DocumentController.handle_remove_pdf()
                    ↓
        AppStateStore.reset_document()
                    ↓
        State updated:
            - doc = None
            - doc_hash = None
            - chat_history = []
                    ↓
        Signal emitted
                    ↓
        UI updates:
            - pdf_info_component cleared
            - chat_history_component cleared

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------